<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="179">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="179">
<taxonomicName authority="Baly, 1860" authorityName="Baly" authorityYear="1860" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Basilepta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Basilepta viridipennis" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="179" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viridipennis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="179">Basilepta viridipennis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 9" captionStartId="F9" captionText="Figure 9. Basilepta viridipennis (Jacoby). a, b. Syntype of Nodostoma occipitale Jacoby, a synonym of B. viridipennis (BMNH); c, d. Colour forms of B. viridipennis." figureDoi="10.3897/dez.66.47447.figure9" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/364595" pageId="0" pageNumber="179" tableDoi="10.3897/dez.66.47447.figure9">Fig. 9</figureCitation>
) has been erroneously reported in the literature as a pest of banana in the Indian Subcontinent (India and Bangladesh), and 
<bibRefCitation author="Waterhouse, DF" journalOrPublisher="21, ACIAR, Canberra" pageId="0" pageNumber="179" publicationUrl="https://www.aciar.gov.au/node/7856" refId="B59" refString="Waterhouse, DF, 1993. The Major Arthropod Pests and Weeds of Agriculture in Southeast Asia: Distribution, Importance and Origin. Monograph No. 21, ACIAR, Canberra" title="The Major Arthropod Pests and Weeds of Agriculture in Southeast Asia: Distribution, Importance and Origin. Monograph No." url="https://www.aciar.gov.au/node/7856" year="1993">Waterhouse (1993)</bibRefCitation>
also listed it as a major pest of banana in Southeast Asia. All reports of its occurrence in northeastern India (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.5958/0974-8172.2018.00226.2" author="Das, D" journalOrPublisher="Indian Journal of Entomology" pageId="0" pageNumber="179" pagination="703 - 705" refId="B12" refString="Das, D, Baruah, K, 2018. Management of banana leaf and fruit scarring beetle Nodostomaviridipennis Motsch. in Assam. Indian Journal of Entomology 80: 703 - 705" title="Management of banana leaf and fruit scarring beetle Nodostomaviridipennis Motsch. in Assam." url="https://doi.org/10.5958/0974-8172.2018.00226.2" volume="80" year="2018">Das and Baruah 2018</bibRefCitation>
), Bangladesh (
<bibRefCitation author="Ahmed, A" journalOrPublisher="Annals of Plant Protection Sciences" pageId="0" pageNumber="179" refId="B3" refString="Ahmed, A, 1963. Notes on the Biology of Banana Leaf and Fruit Beetle, Nodostomaviridipennis Mots. A review of research, Division of Entomology. Published by Agricultural Information Service, Dhaka, 187-190." title="Notes on the Biology of Banana Leaf and Fruit Beetle, Nodostomaviridipennis Mots. A review of research, Division of Entomology. Published by Agricultural Information Service, Dhaka, 187 - 190." year="1963">Ahmed 1963</bibRefCitation>
; 
